OL,6,FTwo care workers who drugged and
OL,7,Fsexually abused a vulnerable child
OL,8,Fthey were supposed to be looking after
OL,9,Fhave been jailed.
OL,11,FLiam Ramsey, 40, and Stephen Hurst,
OL,12,F46, took a 15-year-old into Durham
OL,13,Fcity centre and plied her with wine
OL,14,Fand cocktails, then bought #120 worth
OL,15,Fof class A drugs which they gave to
OL,16,Fher back at the care home.
OL,18,FThe victim later told police that
OL,19,Fbecause of all the cocaine they had
OL,20,Fgiven her last October, she had a
OL,21,Fnosebleed and went upstairs.
