OL,6,FThe men both entered her room naked
OL,7,Fand subjected her to physical and
OL,8,Fsexual abuse throughout the night, and
OL,9,Finto the next morning.
OL,11,FThe men were on duty at the time of
OL,12,Fthe offences, being her carers for the
OL,13,Fday, Durham Police said.
OL,15,FThe victim told police about her
OL,16,Fordeal and the carers were arrested
OL,17,Fand charged with a range of offences,
OL,18,Fincluding sexual activity with a
OL,19,Fchild, intentional strangulation and
OL,20,Fsupply of a class A drug.
