OL,6,F"I would like to commend her for her
OL,7,Fbravery in coming forward and standing
OL,8,Fup against her perpetrators who can no
OL,9,Flonger pose any danger to other
OL,10,Fchildren."
OL,12,FFollowing a trial, Ramsey, of
OL,13,FSunderland, was jailed for 11 years,
OL,14,Fwhilst Hurst, from Richmond, was
OL,15,Fjailed for nine years.
OL,17,FBoth will be on the sex offenders'
OL,18,Fregister for life after they were
OL,19,Fsentenced on Friday at Teesside Crown
OL,20,FCourt.
